== Test Harness  for simple_update_field

Check out the  repository and run bundler
{{{
bundle
}}}

this will download the latest version of simple_update_field from master.


after starting the server
{{{
$ rails server
}}}

The jasmine Test specs are located here

http://localhost:3000/jasmine 


if you want to check a demo of the app - load the seed data

{{{
$ rake db:seed
}}}

and visit http://localhost:3000/phrases
